#. <section class="sutta" id="sn37.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Kodhanasutta"
msgstr "5. Angry"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.5:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā anuruddho bhagavantaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha, sat down to one side, and "
"said to him:"

msgctxt "sn37.5:1.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mātugāmaṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ "
"nirayaṃ upapajjantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see "
"that a female—when her body breaks up, after death—is reborn in a place of "
"loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn37.5:1.3"
msgid ""
"Katīhi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a place of "
"loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.241"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, "
"after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the "
"underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn37.5:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "sn37.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Assaddho ca hoti, ahiriko ca hoti, anottappī ca hoti, kodhano ca hoti, "
"duppañño ca hoti—"
msgstr "They’re faithless, shameless, imprudent, angry, and witless."

msgctxt "sn37.5:2.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after "
"death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, "
"hell.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.5:2.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
